        "content": "<p>I have the following equality (extracted from the 'equational' project, so there's no way to avoid actually proving this),<br>\nwhich represents cancelling out all of the 'x' and '-x' terms that are nested within the same depth. I came up with a really horrible sequence of 'sub_sub', 'add_comm', and 'add_assoc' that achieves it:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">abbrev</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→₀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℚ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">opaque</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">):</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cancel_some_terms</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">):</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">))))))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)))))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">repeat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">conv</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">lhs</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">pattern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sub_sub</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sub_sub</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">add_assoc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is there any tactic or combination of tactics that can simplify this? Ideally, it would notice that there are 'x' and '_ - x' terms buried within a combination of addition and subtraction expressions, and \"push\" all of the x terms to the left with associativity/commutativity/sub_eq_neg_add)</p>",
